data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
INSTRUCTIONS:
WebSockets sends messages to the specified URL, allowing other applications to trigger events accordingly. These messages are based on ASC actions (AutoStart, AutoReset, AutoSplit, AutoHit)
Warning: Start is triggered every when timer start, Reset on resetFlags or ResetHCM run
Recommendation: Use the default message formats when developing applications that integrate with ASC for future compatibility."
NOTE: If ASC receives a message exactly matching the one set as “SPLIT | Message Send”, it will perform a Split. The same applies to Start, Hit, and Reset.
